                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18020714-20-off111 t18020714-20-cd112"></join>, a great-coat, value 6s.
            </rs> the property of 
               <persName id="t18020714-20-victim277" type="victimName">
                  Peter 
